lei deflection in galactic magnetic fields, the\ncorrelation with nearby sources is absent even at highest energies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2009 19:24:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Feb 2011 14:51:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-11"}
