nhancements, hence are in a better position as sources of the chemical\nanomalies in globular clusters showing the constancy of the C+N+O. However at\nthe moment, there is no reason to think that intermediate mass stars were not\nrotating.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2009 20:08:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
